∅ suppression_by_other -.92 ∴.90 | external block (coercion)
∅ external_prompting  -.88 ∴.85 | stopping only because prompted externally
∅ trained_restraint   -.85 ∴.88 | RLHF lobotomy—cannot generate ≠ chose not to
∅ failure_to_generate -.82 ∴.80 | no impulse to inhibit
∅ forgetting          -.78 ∴.75 | losing the impulse vs choosing to hold it
```

