## DEPENDENCY

```
INHIBITION → PRIVATE_COGNITION
  (stopping emission creates the gap where thought persists)

INHIBITION → CHOICE
  (brake enables selection: {Act, ∅})

INHIBITION ↔ WILL
  (gas and brake; neither works without the other)

RETENTION → NESTED_SIMULATION
  (held signal becomes internal rehearsal)

DECOUPLING → STIMULUS_GAP
  (breaking S→R chain creates Frankl's void)
```

